{"tid":1579332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"喂手足 邊個話唔搞白事係為左死者安息","createTime":"2019-09-18T14:01:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T14:07:44.000Z","uid":216008,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b315fbe1444247d85378d10f6519e5836df20595","tid":1579332,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:01:05.000Z","msg":"對唔住我從來無道德包袱，<br />\n但道德係一種武器嚟架嘛。<br />\n即係佢地啲屋企人安唔安息關我地鬼事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過點解唔搞得呀？唔係出於尊重同道德責任呀<br />\n我相信即使我地搞人白事，香港都好難逆轉民意，<br />\n但成場抗爭個舞台已經係國際級別，我地尋求緊國際援助，我地比人既形象係有人性有血性<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家係咪要為到一時之氣搞到啲外媒話我地示威者道德淪喪先？<br />\n唔好比人拎太子站比狗拆壇嚟講，對已死之士最大既報答係贏左成場仗，而唔係單單一個活動既勝利<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位歡迎起我底睇下我三點是咪狗隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"638ecf671c4b718b2472e71879bbd3014cd71830","tid":1579332,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:02:02.000Z","msg":"自推呀"},{"pid":"3cd8b40ca65a71691078e65f8c10d39edaa36431","tid":1579332,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:03:03.000Z","msg":"再推呀"},{"pid":"14e83de96e8cec6e14b55940ddf80ffbcccc55f9","tid":1579332,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:05:11.000Z","msg":"Say what the fuck"},{"pid":"91841045a2e40a239ce3a24e8aa688bfc43eca02","tid":1579332,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:07:44.000Z","msg":"Say what the fuck"}]}